\mt2 Moęž‰foęž‰s Andeb We Foęž‰l Eyoęž‰  
\mt1 Timoti  
\mt2 Emoęž‰ Saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰  
\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ we  
\ip Foęž‰l e dibolo aya silikiyoęž‰, e somaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma dowab aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we Timotimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Moęž‰foęž‰s saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ us aęž‰namioęž‰ to noloęž‰ daęž‰lab. Nowoęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, Timoti e Yaęž‰su Kelisowa ege dowaki, ene tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, hagugu saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. To nowoęž‰ we, Timoti e Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa halale widaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰ki, towoęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, to nowoęž‰ we. Yaęž‰su Kelisowoęž‰ sagalemaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Timoti eyoęž‰ nanogoęž‰ dinafa halale dimaęž‰ki saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Foloęž‰ dibolo aya silikiyoęž‰, noloęž‰ e taęž‰taęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰nabikiyoęž‰, e foęž‰foęž‰doloęž‰ sen koęž‰loęž‰, Timotiyoęž‰ e baęž‰baęž‰ menaęž‰ki, moęž‰foęž‰s we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Ne Foęž‰l, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ ne. Kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimiaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki, Godeyaęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ ne to aęž‰noęž‰ walamaęž‰ki, ne aęž‰na daęž‰feaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ iligaęž‰foęž‰.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1.2 \xt Ilig 16.1, 1Tim 1.2\x*Timoti ge, ni soęž‰wale oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowoęž‰. Moęž‰foęž‰s we gemoęž‰ iligaęž‰toęž‰l. Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ nili Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan manoęž‰, nofolanoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰sa dowanoęž‰ geloęž‰ dimaęž‰ki, Godemoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.   
\s1 Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ wi amioęž‰ moęž‰sende domaęž‰ki, halale sioęž‰  
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 1.3 \xt Ilig 23.1\x*Ne maęž‰mu iyaęž‰loęž‰ Gode kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen aumboęž‰, niyoęž‰loęž‰ asugoęž‰ goęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ dowaki, Godeyaęž‰ ene nanog dimidaęž‰likiyoęž‰, hoęž‰lenowoęž‰loęž‰ nuluwoęž‰loęž‰ niyoęž‰ ge asulaęž‰likiyoęž‰, Godemoęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen.  
\v 4 Giloęž‰ yaęž‰lakiloęž‰ si hoęž‰n ane aęž‰noęž‰ ne asulaęž‰liki, ge galimaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ alan asulaęž‰sen. Moęž‰woęž‰ niyoęž‰ ge baęž‰dakiyoęž‰, mada alan sagalemaęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1.5 \xt Ilig 16.1\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ giloęž‰ tilidabu hendeleyoęž‰ ne asulakiyoęž‰, tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ tamina gu Lois diaęž‰ goęž‰ Yunes diaęž‰ amioęž‰ elen koęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ ge amioęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab, niyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰l.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1.6 \xt 1Tim 4.14\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ni dagiyaęž‰ golab amioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ boba kelegoęž‰woęž‰ gemoęž‰ dimi koęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ de koęž‰loęž‰ dalifaęž‰nigab amiloęž‰ folan aumboęž‰, boba kelegoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ digidalitakiyoęž‰, ge nanogoęž‰ halale dimidaęž‰bi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1.7 \xt Lom 8.15\x*Gode eyoęž‰ tagilan man aęž‰noęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dimi koęž‰sega, nili mamayoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dowaki, haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ man oęž‰liaęž‰ nili asuloęž‰woęž‰ dinafa tilidomaęž‰noęž‰ man oęž‰liaęž‰, aęž‰noęž‰ nimoęž‰ dimi.   
\p
\v 8 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ wi koęž‰loęž‰ wala saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ sendelowaęž‰soęž‰bo. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ wi amiloęž‰ dibolo toęž‰loloęž‰ kalu ne amioęž‰ ge sendelowaęž‰soęž‰bo. Koęž‰sega giyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ halaidoęž‰wa dowakiyoęž‰, niloęž‰ to nafa widoęž‰ amiloęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ dioęž‰l we aumboęž‰ giyoęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰niki, ne kudu yaęž‰bi.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1.9 \xt Aęž‰fe 2.8-9, Tait 3.5\x*Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasiliakiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ maliloęž‰wa meseaęž‰ki, daęž‰fe alifaęž‰. Aęž‰noęž‰ niliyoęž‰ eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ amima koęž‰sega, eyoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki, enedoęž‰ asulab au daęž‰feyoęž‰. Henfeloęž‰ we oęž‰faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰noęž‰ amioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, nimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ tamina disaęž‰.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1.10 \xt Hibu 2.14\x*Koęž‰sega oęž‰goęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan aęž‰noęž‰ fanda asulumaęž‰kiyoęž‰, niloęž‰ gasiliaęž‰noęž‰, Yaęž‰su Keliso, e mioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, sowan man aęž‰noęž‰ e bidilaki, to nafayoęž‰ niloęž‰wa diaęž‰mioęž‰. To nafa aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ nimoęž‰ dimaęž‰ki, fanda widoęž‰.   
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 1.11 \xt 1Tim 2.7\x*To nafa aęž‰noęž‰ wala samaęž‰ki, Gode eyoęž‰ ne Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to nafaloęž‰ walamaęž‰noęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ ne daęž‰feyoęž‰.  
\v 12 Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidoęž‰ amioęž‰ ne oęž‰goęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰li soęž‰l. Koęž‰sega ne moęž‰sendelowaki halale kagafoęž‰loęž‰l. Moęž‰woęž‰ kalu niloęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰loęž‰l we ne asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, nanog nemoęž‰loęž‰ dimi aęž‰noęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene tili dofoęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, henfeloęž‰ weloęž‰ edab ami aęž‰na taęž‰faęž‰ib, niyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰l.  
\v 13 Man digaloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ niloęž‰ gemoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, giyoęž‰ halale taęž‰li dofoęž‰lubi. Ge Yaęž‰su Kelisowa dowakiyoęž‰, tilidabu man oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1.14 \xt 1Tim 6.20\x*Godeyaęž‰ Mamayoęž‰ ge oęž‰liaęž‰ iliki asuwaęž‰taęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰ to nafale koęž‰loęž‰ gemoęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰kiloęž‰ dimi aęž‰noęž‰, giyoęž‰ dinafa boęž‰foęž‰lubi.   
\p
\v 15 Kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Aęž‰sia hen amiloęž‰ saęž‰sen i aęž‰noęž‰, Figelus oęž‰liaęž‰ Hemogenes oęž‰liaęž‰, iyoęž‰ tambo ne koęž‰loęž‰ gola baęž‰baęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ giyoęž‰ asulufoęž‰lab.   
\p
\v 16 Koęž‰sega Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ Onesifolus oęž‰liaęž‰ ene soęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ nofolaki asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. Moęž‰woęž‰, eyoęž‰ ne haęž‰sa domaęž‰kiyoęž‰ tamin amioęž‰ asufaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, ne dibolowa ane amioęž‰, eyoęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰sendelo alifaęž‰.  
\v 17 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ e Lom faęž‰laęž‰dowakiyoęž‰, ne mada kedaęž‰i yaęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰ neloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰.  
\v 18 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ne Aęž‰fesaęž‰s sen amioęž‰, eloęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ asufaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, giyoęž‰ asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰walilab hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, e nofoloęž‰ alifomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ Yaęž‰sumoęž‰woęž‰ to soęž‰loęž‰l.   
\c 2  
\s1 Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ dimidoęž‰ au, kudu hamana  
\p
\v 1 Ni soęž‰wa Timoti, Yaęž‰su Keliso eloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ge halale alifomaęž‰ki doma.  
\v 2 To niloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amiloęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, giyoęž‰ digaloęž‰ kalu nolboęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰bi. Kalu i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ giloęž‰ widab aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ nolboęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰walamaęž‰ki, imoęž‰woęž‰ to man aęž‰noęž‰ widaęž‰bi.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2.3 \xt 2Tim 1.8\x*Ge Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene ame kalu nafale oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowakiyoęž‰, niloęž‰ nanog hidaęž‰yoęž‰ dioęž‰l we aumboęž‰, giyoęž‰loęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ua diaęž‰bi.  
\v 4 Ame kalu dowab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, eloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan misaęž‰ kalu alan aęž‰noęž‰ sagalemaęž‰kiyoęž‰, e amisaęž‰n amiloęž‰ nanog noloęž‰ moęž‰diaki, nanog imilig aęž‰naka halale domaęž‰ib.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2.5 \xt 2Tim 4.8\x*Aęž‰laęž‰ aumaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, kalu nowoęž‰ heyab amioęž‰ waęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰noęž‰ asulalega, eyoęž‰ heyab amiloęž‰ ele saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰ib. Koęž‰sega eyoęž‰ ele saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰nalega, tiniab amioęž‰ waęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰diaęž‰ib.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2.6 \xt 1Kol 9.7\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ eloęž‰ gelan kalu nanogdoęž‰ halale diab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, fowoęž‰ tulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, heboęž‰ enenoęž‰ tamina boęž‰e diaęž‰ib.  
\v 7 Ge niloęž‰ to soęž‰loęž‰l we dinafa asulaęž‰bi. Moęž‰woęž‰ Alan eyoęž‰ asuloęž‰ nafayoęž‰ gemoęž‰woęž‰ fanda walamaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 8-9 \x - \xo 2.8-9 \xt Lom 1.3, 1Kol 15.4\x*\x - \xo 2.8-9 \xt Aęž‰fe 3.1,13, Fili 1.12-14\x*Yaęž‰su Keliso e sowaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰dasili aęž‰noęž‰, Daęž‰ibidaęž‰ emaęž‰mu koęž‰loęž‰ e asulaęž‰bi. To nafa aęž‰noęž‰ ni widaęž‰len amioęž‰, kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ ne mogagoęž‰ kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, hidaęž‰yoęž‰ noloęž‰ nemoęž‰ dimiaki, ne saęž‰niyaęž‰ melaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, dibolowa toęž‰loloęž‰. Koęž‰sega Godeyaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ saęž‰niyaęž‰yoęž‰ mada moęž‰mele alifaęž‰ib.  
\v 10 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰gasilimaęž‰kiyoęž‰, hidaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ niyoęž‰ oęž‰li diaęž‰noęž‰. Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ wiya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ aęž‰gasiliaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, i aęž‰noęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 2.11 \xt 2Kol 4.11\x*To we hendele saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l.  
\q1 Nioęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰ sowoęž‰lalega,  
\q2 Nioęž‰ e oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ mesaęž‰noęž‰.   
\q1
\v 12 \x - \xo 2.12 \xt Madi 10.33\x*Nioęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ diaęž‰li haęž‰nalega,  
\q2 nioęž‰loęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu mesaęž‰noęž‰.  
\q1 Nioęž‰ e gola baęž‰dalega,  
\q2 Eyoęž‰ nioęž‰loęž‰ gola baęž‰baęž‰ib.   
\q1
\v 13 \x - \xo 2.13 \xt Lom 3.3-4, Tait 1.2\x*Nioęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ asulab aumboęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰nalega,  
\q2 Yaęž‰su Eyoęž‰ ene to saefaęž‰yoęž‰ ka kudu haęž‰naęž‰ib. Moęž‰woęž‰ enedoęž‰ man dimidaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ mada moęž‰taęž‰faęž‰ib.   
\s1 Godeyaęž‰ nanog dian kaluwaęž‰ man nafayoęž‰ we  
\p
\v 14 \x - \xo 2.14 \xt 1Tim 6.4, Tait 3.9\x*Kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ asulufoęž‰meleaęž‰kiyoęž‰ widaęž‰lubi. Iyoęž‰ to amioęž‰ egeleboęž‰ kegabenaęž‰ki, Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ giyoęž‰ hagugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Moęž‰woęž‰ to kegab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰asuwaęž‰talikiyoęž‰, kalu daęž‰daęž‰likiloęž‰ sen aęž‰noęž‰ mogagilaęž‰maęž‰ib.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2.15 \xt 1Tim 4.6\x*Gode eyoęž‰ ge nanog dian kalu nafale aęž‰laęž‰samaęž‰kiyoęž‰, giyoęž‰ ene nanog aęž‰noęž‰ halale diaęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, ge Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ hende digaloęž‰le widalikiyoęž‰ moęž‰sendelomaęž‰ib.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2.16 \xt 1Tim 4.7\x*Ge madali to koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰woęž‰ nenelabdoęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ uayoęž‰ gasa dowaęž‰soęž‰bo. Moęž‰woęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale to oęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰ni haęž‰nab.  
\v 17-18 \x - \xo 2.17-18 \xt 1Tim 1.20\x*Ililoęž‰ to man saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, wagegemaęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ silikiloęž‰ nanalaęž‰liki haęž‰nanoęž‰ aęž‰ngab. Himeneus diaęž‰ Filetus diaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, iyoęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰nab. Aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ to widaęž‰likiyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śNioęž‰ tamina aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasi koęž‰loęž‰ tif amioęž‰ mada moęž‰dasimaęž‰noęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰widaęž‰lab amioęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale nolbaęž‰loęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ noęž‰noloęž‰ alifaęž‰.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 2.19 \xt Nam 16.5, Ais 52.11, Yoęž‰n 10.14, 1Kol 8.3\x*Koęž‰sega Gode eyoęž‰ ene saęž‰soęž‰ dimaęž‰kiyoęž‰, aikoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ geloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, aikoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ mada moęž‰hegemaęž‰ib. Aikoęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ towoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰, â€śKalukaęž‰isale enenoęž‰le aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ Alan eyoęž‰ asuloęž‰.â€ť Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to nowoęž‰ we, â€śKalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Alanaęž‰ wiloęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, mogagoęž‰woęž‰ waęž‰kabiyoęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo.â€ť   
\p
\v 20 A alan us amioęž‰ fafo oęž‰liaęž‰ disi koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na daęž‰lab. Noloęž‰ hen oęž‰liaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ ful oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰na dimidoęž‰, noloęž‰ goęž‰l oęž‰liaęž‰ silba oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰na dimidoęž‰. Noloęž‰ nanog nafale dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ difaęž‰ koęž‰sega, noloęž‰ ba madali wa difaęž‰.  
\v 21 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ ene melaęž‰noęž‰ us amioęž‰ wa daęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ dilalega, e nafale faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, nanog nafaleyoęž‰ oęž‰li dimidamaęž‰ib. E maliloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowab koęž‰loęž‰ Alanaęž‰yoęž‰ ene nanog nafayoęž‰ emoęž‰ dimaęž‰ki taęž‰faęž‰ib. \fig A alan usamioęž‰ fafo oęž‰liaęž‰ disi koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na daęž‰lab.|alt="Various vessels" src="HK00143B.TIF" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles Â© The British & Foreign Bible Society, 1954, 1967, 1972, 1995." ref="2.20" \fig*   
\p
\v 22 \x - \xo 2.22 \xt 1Tim 6.11\x*Uwoęž‰ dian man dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulan aęž‰noęž‰ giyoęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰bi. Hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo man digaloęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ tilidabu man oęž‰liaęž‰, nowoęž‰ asulakiloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan manoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰saloęž‰ domaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi. Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ digaloęž‰likiloęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ wiloęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lab i aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰ dowaki, man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 2.23 \xt 1Tim 4.7\x*Giyoęž‰ moęž‰loęž‰ma kabiloęž‰ towaęž‰loęž‰ kegakiloęž‰ to saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ tiniaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ dowaęž‰bi. Moęž‰woęž‰ to aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ alanoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰ib, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ giyoęž‰ asulab.  
\v 24 Alanaęž‰ ene nanog dian kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ towaęž‰yoęž‰ kegaęž‰soęž‰bo. Koęž‰sega ene manoęž‰ oęž‰m. Eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tambomoęž‰woęž‰ sagale alitaęž‰sen. Eyoęž‰ nolboęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰moęž‰beaki haęž‰sa iliki, dinafa nafale walamaęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab.  
\v 25 Kalukaęž‰isale i nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ e oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gis dimidalikiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene nanog dian kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰sa fanda widaęž‰sen. Moęž‰woęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalu i oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ fogoęž‰ oęž‰li dimialikiyoęž‰, iyoęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ nodolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, to hendeleyoęž‰ oęž‰li fanda asulumaęž‰ki aęž‰laki, eyoęž‰ haęž‰sa dowaki widaęž‰sen.  
\v 26 Kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰yaęž‰ dibolowa disaęž‰foęž‰liki, eloęž‰ asulab au dimidamaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰len koęž‰sega, iyoęž‰ to hendele aęž‰noęž‰ fanda baęž‰dabikiyoęž‰, Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰yaęž‰ dage amiloęž‰ walafoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ sili alifaęž‰ib.   
\c 3  
\s1 Henfeloęž‰ we elemaęž‰nigalikiyoęž‰, hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ modoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 3.1 \xt 1Tim 4.1\x*Hoęž‰len we elemaęž‰nigalikiyoęž‰, man mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ modoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰ giyoęž‰ asulufoęž‰lubi.  
\v 2 Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale ininaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ alan asulaki, moleyoęž‰ mada alan diaęž‰noęž‰ asulumaęž‰ib. Iyoęž‰ to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰ kailaki, noloęž‰ waęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰ib. Soęž‰wayaęž‰yoęž‰ iya oęž‰liaęž‰ ano oęž‰liaęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰iyakiyoęž‰, kalu nolboęž‰woęž‰ sagalakiyoęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ towoęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰maęž‰ib. Iyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab aumboęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰ib.  
\v 3 Kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰disaęž‰maęž‰ib. Kalu nolbaęž‰loęž‰ mogagoęž‰ emoęž‰loęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰gaęž‰lilaęž‰maęž‰ib. Iliyoęž‰ noloęž‰loęž‰ sadaęž‰baęž‰ib. Inin asuloęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰tilidomaęž‰ib. Kalu noloęž‰ moęž‰nofolakiloęž‰ nagaloęž‰ dimiab aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰ligab aęž‰laęž‰asulumaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iliyoęž‰ man nafa oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gis diaęž‰ib.  
\v 4 Kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ ene milileyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ teledomaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iliyoęž‰ moęž‰dinafa asulaki, boęž‰boęž‰gedoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asulumaęž‰ib. Kailan manoęž‰ i amioęž‰ alan domaęž‰ib. Henfeloęž‰ wenamiloęž‰ sagalemaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰naki, iliyoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ moęž‰sagale alifaęž‰ib.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3.5 \xt Madi 7.15,21, Tait 1.16\x*Kalukaęž‰isale iyoęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰ Keliso dowaki, tilidabu hendeleyoęž‰ halaidoęž‰woęž‰ aundoęž‰ma. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ dowaki, uayoęž‰ gasa dowaęž‰soęž‰bo.   
\p
\v 6 Kalu i nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰ noloęž‰ dikidakiyoęž‰, ene a usa haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ silikiyoęž‰, ga asugoęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ eloęž‰ asuloęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ domaęž‰ki, dikili saęž‰maęž‰ib. Ga i aęž‰noęž‰ ene man mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, sendelowoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ e hidaęž‰ alitalikiyoęž‰, asuloęž‰ mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ e susululiaęž‰gaęž‰ siaęž‰lab.  
\v 7 Ga i aęž‰noęž‰ to man hoęž‰gi widab aęž‰noęž‰ mada sagalaęž‰li daęž‰daęž‰sen koęž‰sega, iyoęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ moęž‰fanda asulaęž‰sen.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3.8 \xt Kis 7.11\x*Tamin amioęž‰ Yanes diaęž‰ Yambes diaęž‰maęž‰loęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰s oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ gis di oęž‰leaumboęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ kalu i wemaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ to hendele oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gis diab. Inin asuloęž‰woęž‰ noęž‰noloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰gaki, iyoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰mala tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 9 Koęž‰sega tamin amiloęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰loęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰namiloęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ aumboęž‰, iyoęž‰ noęž‰nolaki dimidoęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale tambowaęž‰yoęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ililoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ alanoęž‰ moęž‰domaęž‰ib.   
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Timotimoęž‰woęž‰ hagugu sioęž‰  
\p
\v 10 Timoti ge, niloęž‰ widaęž‰senoęž‰, ni manoęž‰, niloęž‰ man dimidan moęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, niloęž‰ tilidabuwoęž‰, niloęž‰ haęž‰sa dowan manoęž‰, niloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ manoęž‰, ne hidaęž‰yoęž‰ diaęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ tambo, ge baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ asuloęž‰.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3.11 \xt Ilig 13.14-52, 14.5,8-20\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Antioęž‰g, Aikonium oęž‰liaęž‰ Lista amisaęž‰n aęž‰namiloęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ neloęž‰ amiloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ge asuloęž‰. Koęž‰sega Alanaęž‰yoęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ alan aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ne mogagilabenaęž‰ki, eyoęž‰ ne dinafa asuwaęž‰taęž‰sen.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 3.12 \xt Madi 16.24, Yoęž‰n 15.20, Ilig 14.22\x*Hendele, kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowa tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ man digaloęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰ asulab oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ alanoęž‰ dimiaęž‰melaęž‰ib.  
\v 13 Koęž‰sega kalu mogagoęž‰le aęž‰lab oęž‰liaęž‰ dikili saęž‰lan kalu oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰loęž‰ man dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ mada alan dowaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰ib. Iliyoęž‰ kalu noloęž‰ dikidalikiyoęž‰, nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ iyoęž‰loęž‰ dikidaęž‰melaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 14 Koęž‰sega gemoęž‰loęž‰ to widabiloęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰, ge kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Moęž‰woęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale gemoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ge oęž‰li fanda asuloęž‰.  
\v 15 Ge soęž‰walaęž‰suwa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ mioęž‰ amioęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ to saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ge fanda asululi koęž‰loęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ge Yaęž‰su Kelisowa tilidaęž‰dabikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ge gasilimaęž‰ki, to aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ asuloęž‰ nafayoęž‰ gemoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰li dimiaęž‰ib.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3.16 \xt Lom 15.4\x*Godeyaęž‰ to saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tambo Godeya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, to aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ asuwaęž‰takiyoęž‰, man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ ele baęž‰daęž‰b, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ hala dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ digalelaęž‰b, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iyoęž‰ man digaloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰ki, Godeyaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ widaęž‰len.  
\v 17 Godeyaęž‰ to aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene nanogdoęž‰ dian kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ egoęž‰ dowaki, nanogoęž‰ nafale dimidamaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ to saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ widaęž‰lab. \fig Soęž‰wagalinoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to manoęž‰ fanda widaęž‰lubi.|alt="Teaching children" src="05_De_11_03_RG_gr.tif" size="col" copy="Â© Sweet Publishing http://sweetpublishing.com, licensed under a CC: BY-SA 3.0 Unported licence." ref="3.15" \fig*   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 Yaęž‰su Keliso e henfeloęž‰ weloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰nikiloęž‰ yab amioęž‰, eyoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ sab we oęž‰liaęž‰ sowoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ alobaęž‰maęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰labiki, niyoęž‰ to we gemoęž‰ halale saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l.  
\v 2 Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ widaęž‰lubi. Hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo dimidaliaęž‰bi. Giyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰loęž‰ hala dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ digalaęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iyoęž‰ halale alitaęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidakiyoęž‰, ge haęž‰sa haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ dinafa fanda widaęž‰bi.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 4.3 \xt 1Tim 4.1\x*Tif amioęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale iyoęž‰ to digaloęž‰ hendeleyoęž‰ moęž‰ege daęž‰daki, iloęž‰ iligi daęž‰baęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ to koęž‰li noloęž‰ walamaęž‰ki, widan kalu modoęž‰woęž‰ hoęž‰le kegeaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ aęž‰na daęž‰daęž‰melaęž‰ib.  
\v 4 Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, iyoęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ gola baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, kandayoęž‰ malolab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ tilidaęž‰daki kudu haęž‰naęž‰ib.  
\v 5 Koęž‰sega kelegoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ ge haęž‰sa iliki, alobaęž‰daęž‰bi. Hidaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ yab aęž‰noęž‰ diaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰bi. Kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ giyoęž‰ to nafayoęž‰ widaęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ nanog gemoęž‰loęž‰ dimi aęž‰noęž‰ tambo nafale diaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰ kedelaęž‰bi.   
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 4.6 \xt Fili 2.17\x*Niloęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰l we moęž‰woęž‰, wa hoęž‰noęž‰ boba meakiloęž‰ kolodan aumboęž‰,\f + \fr 4.6 \ft Tamin amioęž‰ boba kelegoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ soęž‰meaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, hoęž‰len nol amioęž‰ iliyoęž‰ wa hoęž‰n aęž‰noęž‰ boba waęž‰la tulan. Man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asulaki bale sioęž‰. (Namba 15.1-12)\f* melaęž‰noęž‰ niloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰kolodaęž‰i haęž‰nab koęž‰loęž‰, ne oęž‰goęž‰ somaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma faęž‰laęž‰dowab.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 4.7 \xt 1Tim 6.12\x*Ne bubaęž‰li haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, mada odoęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰i yaęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰ kagayoęž‰. Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ nemoęž‰loęž‰ dimidamaęž‰kiloęž‰ dimi aęž‰noęž‰ niyoęž‰ diaęž‰i yaęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰ kedetoęž‰l. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ne tilidabuwoęž‰ halale taęž‰li dotaęž‰gaęž‰ mioęž‰.   
\p
\v 8 \x - \xo 4.8 \xt 1Kol 9.24-25\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ henfeloęž‰ weloęž‰ edab amioęž‰, digaleloęž‰ alobaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ kalu, Alan aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ne man digaloęž‰ kudu ane aęž‰na wikilakiyoęž‰, boba kelegoęž‰woęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ imilig nekoęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰ba, koęž‰sega kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰loęž‰ miaęž‰nigab aęž‰noęž‰ sagalaęž‰likiloęž‰ yasilab oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib.   
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Timotiyoęž‰ eloęž‰wa menaęž‰ki sioęž‰  
\p
\v 9 Ge neloęž‰ amioęž‰ miaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, togoęž‰ boęž‰boęž‰ge kedaęž‰bi.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 4.10 \xt Ilig 15.37-39, 2Kol 8.23, Kolo 4.14\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ Demas, e asuloęž‰woęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wena diaęž‰foęž‰len koęž‰loęž‰ ne taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, Tesalonaika aęž‰na ane. Kelesenas e Galasia hena ane aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Taitus e Dalamasia hena ane.  
