\p Ne Godeyaęž‰ nanog dimidab amioęž‰ Mak eyoęž‰ oęž‰li asuwaęž‰faęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰ ge yakiyoęž‰, e tililiaęž‰ yaęž‰bi.  
