\v 14 \x - \xo 4.14 \xt Ais 59.18, Lom 2.6\x*Goęž‰foęž‰ ki amiloęž‰ nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu, Alegsanda eyoęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidaki ne mogagilaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ Alanaęž‰yoęž‰ eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ waęž‰loęž‰ waęž‰demaęž‰ib.  
